# spark-ai

**Cross‑platform AI functions for Apache Spark DataFrames.**

`spark-ai` gives you a clean, Pythonic API to run AI models directly inside Spark
transformations — on your laptop, on EMR, on Kubernetes, or anywhere Apache Spark runs.
No platform lock‑in.

## Installation

```bash
pip install spark-ai
